I would support overthrowing any communist government.  I believe communism is a fundamental violation of the rights of man.  A democracy must also protect the rights of minorities.  Say you had a government installed democratically that believed in killing all people over age 75.  It's a democratically instally government.  I still would support overthrowing it as it violates basic human rights.  Communism does too.<br>
